16:19:50.000Z","msg":"樓主花盡力氣跑到九龍醫院，<br />\n氣急敗壞的向護士查詢他已70多的母親在哪間病房，<br />\n得知後他一股腦的跑到4樓，只見整個4樓滿是比自已年輕的人。<br />\n心急如焚的樓主也沒空管這奇怪境像，<br />\n怱怱向醫生查明母親情況，<br />\n醫生竟面帶笑容的說：「恭喜！恭喜！你做哥哥了！」<br />\n樓主雖然一頭霧水，但心內仍有一股欣喜，<br />\n在場的年輕人大概都為他高興，紛紛拍掌，有些更歡呼起來。<br />\n整個4樓充斥著歡樂氣氛<br />\n樓主走進產房向母親道賀，打趣說：「媽，新爸爸是誰，怎麼我不知道？」<br />\n但母親突然怒吼：「鬼知咩！唔係你個仆街仔係高登開d濕9 亂up post！洗成個四樓都係你個仆街d老豆！生撚死我咩！」"},{"pid":"712cfbe0465e8320ef18a4b91686840c1b4eb540","tid":44740,"uid":488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T16:25:03.000Z","msg":"樓主老母個陰道開始多人 連登仔全面進場"},{"pid":"2758fc424b293e8e19d93743f9ddbc203b6dd9da","tid":44740,"uid":61853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T16:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1lmaqtnz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1lmaqtnz&h=9f98a99e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b44e3045a15ea7abb65390591a9d44cda1108fe","tid":44740,"uid":65984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T16:35:10.000Z","msg":"伯母辛苦哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad20d30b40689f687b503720aa5d08011683f249","tid":44740,"uid":34645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T16:36:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/img/champion/splash/Shaco_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fddragon.leagueoflegends.com%2Fcdn%2Fimg%2Fchampion%2Fsplash%2FShaco_0.jpg&h=acbc31e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a41f0a2afd8d26a96e311eb0c3882ee59b167587","tid":44740,"uid":19502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T16:45:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p5410Rk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp5410Rk.jpg&h=e29a9723&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img s